# Project Overview

Enterprise-ready F&B Table Booking & Ordering Web App.

## Key Non-Negotiables
- **Zero double-bookings** via Redis distributed locks
- **ACID transactions** for every booking/payment mutation
- **Real-time** kitchen/POS sync via Socket.IO
- **Mobile-first, pixel-perfect** UI with Shadcn + TailwindCSS

## Monorepo Layout

```
/
├── apps/
│   ├── web/          # Next.js 14 App Router frontend
│   └── api/          # NestJS backend
├── packages/
│   └── shared/       # Shared Zod schemas, TS types, constants
├── docker-compose.yml
└── .cursor/rules/
```

## Package Responsibilities
| Package | Tech | Responsibility |
|---|---|---|
| `apps/web` | Next.js, Tailwind, Shadcn, Zustand, TanStack Query | UI, routing, client state |
| `apps/api` | NestJS, Prisma, Redis, Socket.IO | Business logic, DB, realtime |
| `packages/shared` | Zod, TypeScript | Contracts shared between web & api |

## Naming Conventions
- Files: `kebab-case` everywhere
- React components: `PascalCase`
- NestJS classes: `PascalCase`; services/controllers end in `Service`/`Controller`
- DB models: `PascalCase` (Prisma); table names `snake_case`
- Env vars: `SCREAMING_SNAKE_CASE`

## Imports
- Always use path aliases (`@web/`, `@api/`, `@shared/`) — never relative `../../`
